{"tid":1267901,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(多圖) 1997年6月30號 香港回歸前嘅一日","createTime":"2019-06-30T06:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T07:50:14.000Z","uid":7458,"like":83,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"80645cafb87bf78dbeae0bd2e8bc62e7e47ffe5a","tid":1267901,"uid":7458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T06:22:17.000Z","msg":"話咁快就已經22年 好多人都應該仲記得當時嘅情況 <br />\n當我而家睇返呢d相 我先發現原來香港以前係咁輝煌<br />\n當時有人係好唔捨得 同時又有人覺得好開心回歸<br />\n唔知而家嘅佢地仲係咪有同樣嘅諗法呢? <br />\n而家長大後嘅你見到香港變成咁又有咩感想? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多 一齊睇下當時嘅情況<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ToBU8KA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FToBU8KA.jpg&h=55ff3a59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cyfiQXX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcyfiQXX.jpg&h=6d0aef78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/42icVpC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F42icVpC.jpg&h=1f977167&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ca0rfpD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fca0rfpD.jpg&h=458dbb32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MHe7Kh0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMHe7Kh0.jpg&h=f1ffb8a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7vjohC1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7vjohC1.jpg&h=ecb537c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KGuLvX2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKGuLvX2.jpg&h=0e4fd04a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eu9caX3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEu9caX3.jpg&h=8b24c6c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MMCttKK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=ht